Fitting the distributions

Themisto Abuysorum

My measurements are from 3 stations. Gamma distributions ok for most measurements. Not very representative for the larger individuals. I was not able to identify smaller species so I likely only measured the larger ones‚Ä¶ i think too much bias to use my data. I combined my data with the multi-net measurements done by a professional. The data from the multinet has avoidance issues and is likely biased.
